race.description: Mayhem In The Mounting Yard 21st Nov Mdn Plate
race.comment: ALPINE COWGIRL (3) progressed nicely missing by 1.3L over 1400m at this track. She is still well shy of her Victorian best and the step up to the mile is ideal. Has the inside barrier and will be tough to beat. JUDGE JENNI (7) switched from a Victorian yard and went close here over 1420m five days ago. She was backed off the map and Darmanin stays aboard. Positions forward and on the quick return rates a big threat. SWING LOW (9) hasn't gone close to recapturing her early Victorian form, but she jumped $4 here last time suggesting improvement was in store. She got too far back again but the mile will suit and she's worth including at odds. CAFFY (5) is also a minor hope. Peaks this evening and the in-form hoop replaces the apprentice.
